  "remarks": "Bank Refah Kargaran is an Iranian bank with links to the Government of Iran. It cooperates with, among others, the Ministry of Defense and Armed Forces Logistics (MODAFL), including by facilitating the purchase of weapons. It also cooperates with the Ministry of Economy and Finance and the Ministry of Health.",
